def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('0', 'H0')

print(insert_before_character('10 test 20')) # 1H0 test 20
print(insert_before_character('100 test 200')) # 1H00 test 200
print(insert_before_character('Hello World!')) # Hello World!
print(insert_before_character('This is an example')) # This is an example
